<div id="stitle" style="display:none;">Letter</div>
<div class="nbunit" id="a26Jul1927"><font color="red">26 July 1927</font> <i>Selected Letters</i> (to Harriet Weaver): I am glad you got the booklet [Pomes Penyeach]  &hellip; Miss Beach and Miss Monnier have gone to Savoy &hellip; More kilos of abuse about <font face="wake">w</font> &hellip;  I enclose [enclosed] an explanation of one of the added phrases on p. 1 of last instalment [L&apos;Arcs en His Cieling Flee Chinx on the Flur.]  </div>
